          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6696620-c-lia-loureiro?shelf=lus%C3%B3fonos-lusophone">lusÃ³fonos-lusophone</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6696620-c-lia-loureiro?shelf=wishlist">wishlist</a>
